    "_comment_purpose": "Canonical Leo / fresh-machine MCP server template. Mirrors operator's ~/.claude/.mcp.json structure (server names + commands) but redacts operator-private env values. Leo fills in API keys + paths after install. Copy to ~/.claude/.mcp.json then restart Claude Code.",
    "_comment_doctrine": "See _shared-memory/knowledge/leo-auto-setup-doctrine-2026-05-25.md + _shared-memory/knowledge/sanctioned-bypasses-doctrine-2026-05-21.md. Never push operator's real credentials. Path placeholders use FILL-IN-PATH or rely on SINISTER_SANCTUM_ROOT env. Set env vars via Wizard step 3 (git config user.name) or via setx ANTHROPIC_API_KEY ...",
